Package: mariner
Type: Package
Title: Mariner: Explore the Hi-Cs
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Eric", "Davis", role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "ericscottdavis@outlook.com",
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4051-3217"))
  )
Description: Tools for manipulating paired ranges and
    working with Hi-C data in R. Functionality includes
    manipulating/merging paired regions, generating
    paired ranges, extracting/aggregating interactions
    from `.hic` files, and visualizing the results. 
    Designed for compatibility with plotgardener for
    visualization.
